{"tid":560423,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"集思廣益 翻工有個pt妹妹幾啱傾有咩計仔抄牌而唔odd","createTime":"2018-02-14T05:43:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T09:14:24.000Z","uid":123962,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b45cb7cb27555d6095035ddafc75abc206dc3ebe","tid":560423,"uid":123962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:43:56.000Z","msg":"我飲食邊啲pt翻工唔定 所以都唔知幾時先見一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以想諗個唔awkward既方法keep個contact <br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢多數都羣一兩個fd翻同埋我地係公司飯堂食個飯之後開工 <br />\n不過上次佢冇fd就自己坐埋我面前 有fd就跟翻fd<br />\n佢本身係多嘢講既人對個個都up得下 而我死毒拎 <br />\n但我係少數同佢同齡人 又好似同我比較多嘢講 相對其他同齡 除咗佢fd<br />\n我地行過都撩下大家一兩句咁<br />\n順便再問點應對佢啲好是但擺明r嘢講既問題/短句例如仲以為你收咗工 乜你未收工 去咗搞咩。。。etc<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8263bd2779b75fb36ef85dbe9ac542266f137814","tid":560423,"uid":133473,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:45:53.000Z","msg":"on99"},{"pid":"be30a6ff8177c4c0f1d23aa91f630d96b69e290e","tid":560423,"uid":26959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"同佢傾下史達寧琴晚既表現👶🏿"},{"pid":"a895f9fb1b629500904634f77fbf1ed8a31b7860","tid":560423,"uid":64145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:53:49.000Z","msg":"果d 問題你咪照直答囉，唔係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fb5660771566c5a933f8d488138ae62241894fb","tid":560423,"uid":123962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be30a6ff8177c4c0f1d23aa91f630d96b69e290e","tid":560423,"uid":26959,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:49:41.000Z","msg":"同佢傾下史達寧琴晚既表現👶🏿"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-14T05:58:04.000Z","msg":"我這樣討論"},{"pid":"5dc8c326b7be6bcfcf40f6b5dc2e7aaa535ac564","tid":560423,"uid":123962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a895f9fb1b629500904634f77fbf1ed8a31b7860","tid":56